summary: This document is a certificate of incorporation for 'JEGE, INC.' filed in the State of Delaware. It certifies that the incorporation was completed on September 7, 2000, and a copy has been forwarded to the New Castle County Recorder of Deeds.
keyFacts: The document certifies the incorporation of 'JEGE, INC.'
The incorporation was filed on September 7, 2000.
A filed copy was forwarded to the New Castle County Recorder of Deeds.
The document is marked as confidential.
